<subSubSection id="C32E65060917FFBFFF51F7D4FD2CFD16" pageId="9" pageNumber="110" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8B368D0917FFBFFF51F7D4FF50FDA9" blockId="9.[130,775,503,688]" box="[132,196,503,529]" pageId="9" pageNumber="110">NOTE</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8B368D0917FFBFFF51F434FD2CFD16" blockId="9.[130,775,503,688]" pageId="9" pageNumber="110">
Les échantillons appartenant à la récolte 
<emphasis id="B940EA9F0917FFBFFDF5F435FD23FD96" box="[544,695,534,560]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="110">Deplanche 328</emphasis>
mêlent deux espèces.Ils correspondent tous aux caractères florifères cités dans la diagnose originale de 
<taxonomicName id="4C344D0E0917FFBFFE73F475FD15FDD6" box="[422,641,598,624]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Nephrodesmus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="9" pageNumber="110" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sericeus">
<emphasis id="B940EA9F0917FFBFFE73F475FD15FDD6" box="[422,641,598,624]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="110">Nephrodesmus sericeus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
à l’exception du spécimen de P (P02296554), en fruit, qui est un isotype de 
<taxonomicName id="4C344D0E0917FFBFFF56F4B5FEE9FD16" box="[131,381,662,688]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Arthroclianthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="9" pageNumber="110" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="obovatus">
<emphasis id="B940EA9F0917FFBFFF56F4B5FEE9FD16" box="[131,381,662,688]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="110">Arthroclianthus obovatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(voir Note sous cette espèce).
</paragraph>
